title: # 23 – Something’s Burning Uncut – Michelle Wolf & Bobby Kelly
description:
Something’s Burning Uncut is the uncut audio from my cooking show “Something’s Burning” on YouTube.

On this episode that originally aired on YouTube Jun 24, 2019, Bobby Kelly & Michelle Wolf hang out while I make a cheesy biscuit eggs benedict.
